            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>✠ In nomine Domini. Tenporibus [domni] Clementi[s pa]pe sede primo,
                        [inperante] domno Henrico in Italia [a]nno primo, die tertjo m(ense)
                        februarii, indiccione quintade[ci]ma, <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >Rav(enne)</placeName>, in superi[o]ra domi que est iusta <rs
                            key="#Churches">hecclesia</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">mon(asterii)</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1480">Sancti
                            Stefani qui vocatur Maioris</orgName>. Dum ibi inventi fuissent bonorum
                        [...] hominum idest: <persName key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#people/1596">Mainardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> at[que]
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abb(as)</rs> regule mon(asterii) <orgName
                                key="#Penalty #Cisterns/pits #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie qui
                            vocatur in <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>,
                        <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Iohannes">Ioh(anne)[s]</name></persName>
                        presbiter et monachus eiusdem et <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> item presbiter et
                        monachus, <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Venerandus">Venerandus</name></persName> monachus, 
                        <persName><name ref="Andreas">Handreas</name></persName> magister mil[itum] et 
                        <persName><name ref="Petrus">P[etr]us</name></persName>
                        consanguineo eius, <persName><name ref="Honestus">Honestus</name></persName>
                        [filius] <persName><name ref="Iohannes Lemotio">Ioh(anni)s Lemotjo</name></persName> et alio 
                        <persName><name ref="Honestus de Fuscardo">Honestus de
                            Fuscar[do]</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Petrus/Corbulo">Petrus qui vocatur Corbulo</name></persName>
                        et filii eius, Tas[...] filio eius et
                        me press(ente) <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> <rs key="#Tabellio">tabell(io)</rs>,
                        in [nostro]rum suprascriptorum omnium
                        press(encia) haccesserunt suprascripto Andreas, huna cum Petro
                        consanguine[o] eius, et aprehendiderunt vir[g]a in manibus illorum et
                        misserunt eam in manu suprascripto Mainardus abbas, ec dixeru[nt]:
                        ‘Henspondimus et obl[i]gamus nos nostrosque fili[os] et nepotes vobis
                        suprascripto Mainardus [a]bb[as vestrisque] sucessoribus de medietatem in
                        int(egro) de <rs key="#Cisterns/pits">p[uteo]</rs> qui est retro clausure vestre domnicate quem a[t]
                        vestris reservastis manibus; hab hac ora in antea adiutores vo[s] esse
                        debemus ad abendum, [ten]endu[m] vel defendendum. Et si quis ex nobis vel
                        aliquis ex nostris aliquo damno vobis exinde fecerimus, postquam a vobis
                        requisiti fuerimus, et si infra hocto die non emendaverimus, tunc daturi nos
                        esse promittimus unusquisque, huna cum nostris filiis et nepotibus, vobis
                        vestrisque sucessoribus <rs key="#Penalty">auri obtimi huntjas duas</rs>’. Tunc suprascripto
                        Mainardus abbas, ita hactjpiens, rogavit nos omnes pro futuro testimonio. ✠
                        Ego [P]etrus q(ui) v(ocatur) Corbulo int(er)fui et s(ub)s(cripsi). (C) Ego
                        Guarinus filius Petri in hac sponsione et obbligatione int(er)fui [et
                        subscripsi].</ab>
